node.text: Long before there was @teachertrauma, there was “Paul’s Mom.” It was my way to vent and ended up hitting too close to home for many 😂 Enjoy.

node.text: Trying to bring some laughter on a stressful election night. I present...Paul’s mom at virtual parent teacher conferences. Paul has opted to learn at home this year. Enjoy!

node.title: Paul’s Mom at Virtual Parent-Teacher Conferences

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Trauma on September 04, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Me when someone says there's free food in the staff room: @teachertrauma'.

node.text:
If it’s free, it’s for me! 🍩
.
.
.
.
#teach #teacher #teachers #teachersofinstagram #teachersfollowteachers #teachermemes #teacherhumor #teacherlife #teachersofig

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Trauma on September 02, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Me: I am DONE buying things for my classroom Labor Day weekend sales: @teachertrauma PEEK-A-BOO'.

Photo by Teacher Trauma on September 01, 2021. May be a meme of 3 people and text that says 'Me when someone asks me why I need to take a nap every day after school: @teachertrauma MY BODY IS TIRED. MY MIND MED. IS TIRED. MY SOUL SOULISJUST JUST TIRED.'.

Photo by Teacher Trauma on August 31, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Me when a student is telling me about a fight that they had with their friend and I have to pretend that I haven't heard about it already: @teachertrauma'.

node.text:
As one of the few female teachers in the middle school wing, I am the resident listener of drama and keeper of tea 😂
.
.
.
.
#teach #teacher #teachers #teachersofinstagram #teachersfollowteachers #teachermemes #teacherhumor #teacherlife #teacherproblems

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Trauma on August 30, 2021. May be a meme of 4 people and text that says '@teachertrauma Fuck you Virtual learning Fuck you Teaching while wearing a mask You're cool Shortened school day And fuck you i'm out Kids turning in blank Google documents'.

node.text:
Most things about pandemic teaching suck but those shortened school dayssss thooooo 👀👀 Back to full days now!
.
.
.
.
#teach #teacher #teachers #teachersofinstagram #teachersfollowteachers #teachermemes #teacherproblems #teacherhumor #teacherlife #teacherproblems #teachersofig #pandemicteaching

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Trauma on August 29, 2021. May be a meme of 1 person and text that says 'Me when I'm out with my friends at the end of the summer and they notice me disassociating: @teachertrauma IWAS JUST HAVINGAQUIET QUIET MOMENT OF DESPAIR.'.

node.text:
It’s not the kids or even the adults…it’s the waking up at 6am, having to figure out what I’m packing for lunch every day and the constant hamster wheel of endless work that causes my soul to leave my body 😂
.
.
.
.
#teach #teacher #teachers #teachersofinstagram #teachersfollowteachers #teacherproblems #teacherlife #teachersofig #teachermemes #teacherhumor

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Trauma on August 28, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Me when my friends ask me how I manage not to curse in front of my students: @teachertrauma I have multiple personalities, which is KELLYANNE CHALLENGE SEASON really exhausting. BESTFNS 2ND PLACE BEST'.

Photo shared by Teacher Trauma on August 27, 2021 tagging @jonasbrothers. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Me when I put on music for a dance party brain break and they just sit there: xfinity @teachertrauma Get on your feet for the Jon'as Brothers!'.

node.text:
In this classroom we get on our damn feet for the Jo Bros 😂 What’s your classes go to jam? We also go pretty hard for Lizzo. 
.
.
.
.
#teach #teacher #teachers #teachersofinstagram #teachersfollowteachers #teachermemes #teacherproblems #teacherhumor #teacherlife @jonasbrothers

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Trauma on August 26, 2021. May be an image of 4 people and text that says 'Me trying to explain how much I love my colleagues to someone who doesn't work at my school: @teachertrauma Labood E DUPET It's an iconic friendship for the ages.'.

node.text:
I’m legit obsessed with most of my colleagues. I hope you guys can relate to this because having a support system at school is soooo important and key for survival! 👯‍♀️👫Tag your school crew!
.
.
.
.
#teach #teacher #teachers #teachersofinstagram #teachersfollowteachers #teachermemes #teacherlife #teachersofig

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Trauma on August 25, 2021. May be an image of 4 people and text that says 'Teachers meeting their virtual students in person for the first time: @teachertrauma I'm from thè' Internet.'.

node.text:
Hey! Remember me? Face from a tiny box? What’s upppppp!! 
.
.
.
.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Trauma on August 24, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Teachers when everything they suggest at the staff meeting gets aggressively turned down: @teachertrauma Why am I even here?'.

node.text:

.

.
